headline: QuantumScape Q4 Earnings Call Highlights
summary: QuantumScape (NYSE:QS) used its fourth-quarter and full-year 2025 earnings call to highlight progress on its solid-state battery commercialization roadmap, emphasizing the rollout of its Cobra manufacturing process, pilot-line buildout for QSE-5 cells, and expansion of its partner and customer base.
